    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but the suffering is the point though. if the world is just going to turn into a wasteland, why should i force myself to endure the slow decay of everything i care about? i feel like i'm just waiting for a death that's already inevitable. wouldn't it be more peaceful to just... opt out now, instead of watching it all burn for the next few decades?",
